<h1> Info </h1>
<p>
Hydra is an open-source digital asset management system that utilizes Fedora repository
software to store digital content, and a Solr index for searching.
</p>

<h1>Recent Activity</h1>
<table class="table table-condensed table-striped">
<% @activities.each do |activity| %>
  <tr>
	  <td><%= activity.key %></td>
    <td><%= activity.parameters %></td>
  </tr>
<% end %>
</table>

<h1> Uses </h1>
<p>
Museum staff may request downloaded copies of any file for use with Musuem-related projects
or for use with outside members of the media, such as requests for video content
from news agencies.
</p>
<p>
If you need copies of video or have questions regarding using Hydra, please contact
the library staff at <%= mail_to("library@rockhall.org") %>
</p>